---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section style="padding: 48px 24px;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 720px;">
      <h1 style="color: var(--deep-lake); margin-bottom: 24px;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 32px;">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">1. Data We Collect</h2>
      <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <li><strong>Account information:</strong> Email address, display name, and optional location.</li>
        <li><strong>Catch reports:</strong> Species, weight, bait, rig, venue, conditions, and timestamps you submit.</li>
        <li><strong>Photos:</strong> Images you upload with your catch reports. EXIF metadata (including GPS coordinates) is automatically stripped on upload for your privacy.</li>
        <li><strong>Messages:</strong> Text content sent within group chats.</li>
        <li><strong>Device tokens:</strong> Firebase Cloud Messaging tokens for push notifications.</li>
        <li><strong>Subscription data:</strong> Managed by RevenueCat; we receive subscription status but not payment card details.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <li>To provide the core service: catch logging, group management, and messaging.</li>
        <li>To sync data across your devices via our offline-first architecture.</li>
        <li>To send push notifications about group activity you're subscribed to.</li>
        <li>To generate AI-powered fishing insights (aggregated, anonymised patterns).</li>
        <li>To manage your subscription status.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">3. Photo Privacy</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
        All photos are processed through our upload pipeline which strips EXIF metadata — including GPS
        coordinates, camera model, and timestamps — before permanent storage. Photos are stored on
        Cloudflare R2 with access controlled via time-limited presigned URLs.
      </p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">4. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
        We do not sell your data. Your catch reports and messages are only visible to members of the
        groups you belong to. We share data with the following service providers solely to operate the app:
      </p>
      <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <li><strong>Supabase:</strong> Database and authentication hosting.</li>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Photo storage (R2) and marketing site hosting.</li>
        <li><strong>Firebase:</strong> Push notification delivery.</li>
        <li><strong>RevenueCat:</strong> Subscription management.</li>
        <li><strong>OpenWeather:</strong> Weather data enrichment for catch reports.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">5. Data Retention</h2>
      <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <li>Account data is retained while your account is active.</li>
        <li>Stale device tokens are automatically pruned after 60 days of inactivity.</li>
        <li>You may request deletion of your account and all associated data at any time.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">6. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">If you are in the EU/EEA, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <li>Access your personal data.</li>
        <li>Rectify inaccurate data.</li>
        <li>Request erasure of your data.</li>
        <li>Object to or restrict processing.</li>
        <li>Data portability.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@carp.network">privacy@carp.network</a> to exercise these rights.</p>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px;">7. Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related enquiries: <a href="mailto:privacy@carp.network">privacy@carp.network</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
